<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-3">

        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 125%;">Explore</h5>
            <p style="opacity: 0.5; font-size: 90%;">
              This page is where you can find friends, explore different post, interact with new people and chat about
              what interest you, this could be either studies, going out, meet up or even more, the power is in your hands with
              this one, just go wild, meet friends and have fun.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">



             <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 130%;">Activities</h5>

                <span style="color: darkblue;">Societies</span><br>
                <p> With the Socielties, you get to meet a wide range of different students that attent the university. These students also are seeking to try something new
                  and to make new frirends, some of the societies we include are: Football, Rugby, Boxing, Anime Society and much much more. Why wait!</p>
                <a href="">Join Now</a>

                <br>

                 <br>
                <span style="color: darkblue;">Volunteering</span><br>
                <p> With our Volunteering group, this give our students a change to interact within the university by helping out within a widw range of different fields,
                with this you have the change to learn different skills and develop your communication skills if needed. We Also offer year to year trips to different parts
                of the world where you can help others as well. To Find out more:</p>
                <a href="">Sign Up Now</a><br>

          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
        <%= render '/postcomponents/post_form' %><% if user_signed_in? %> <br> <% end %> <br>

        <% for @p in @post %>
        <div class="panel panel-default post-panel">
          <div class="panel-body row">

            <div class="col-sm-1">
              <img src="\avatar1.png" class="rounded-img" height="50px" width="50px"></img>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-11">
              <p class="post-title"><span class="post-owner"><a href="/user/<%= User.find(@p.user_id).username %>"><%= User.find(@p.user_id).username %></a></span> <span class="post-creation">- <%= @p.created_at.to_formatted_s(:short) %></span></p>
              <p class="post-content"><%= @p.content %></p>
            </div>


          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>


    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">
             <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 125%;">Who to follow</h5>
             <% for @u in @toFollow do %>
               <p style="font-weight: bold; opacity: 0.85;" ><a href="/user/<%= @u.username %>"><%= @u.username %></a></p>
             <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

